precis:
Enactment of the SEIZED PROPERTY DISPOSITION REGULATIONS respecting the
manner in which the Government may dispose of seized property, by public
auction or tender or otherwise, and the calculation of the net proceeds of
disposition to be credited to the Proceeds Account.
